window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>At the heart of Audible's three year partnership with the London Academy of Music and Dramatic Arts (LAMDA) is the involvement of LAMDA students in the creative process of making new audio dramas especially for young people.</p> <p>After the success of GNR8 (Series 1) last year, another four original audio dramas were commissioned from some of the UKâ€™s most exciting emerging writers. The dramas were workshopped with LAMDA students and these final productions were recorded by graduating third years.</p> <p>The result is four brilliantly unique dramas for a new generation that speak to the complex times we live in. We hope you enjoy listening to GNR8!</p>"; 
